==Pledge to the Texas flag== A [[Flag of Texas#Pledge of allegiance|pledge of allegiance to the Texas flag]] was established in 1933.
{{poemquote| Honor the Texas flag; I pledge allegiance to thee, Texas, one state under God, one and indivisible.<ref>[http://www.tsl.state.tx.us/ref/abouttx/flagpledge.html Texas State Library] Flag Pledge, Texas State Library</ref>}}
